00:26:53.190 --> 00:26:56.820
and if it's poorly preserved, okay, it's poorly preserved,

641
00:26:56.820 --> 00:27:00.000
it's not put on ice right way, it's poorly preserved,

642
00:27:00.000 --> 00:27:02.700
there'll be muscle breakdown in the fish.

