00:27:28.830 --> 00:27:30.750
You can treat it with H1 and H2 blockers

652
00:27:30.750 --> 00:27:32.550
and it goes away after a couple hours.

653
00:27:32.550 --> 00:27:34.650
That's scombroid poisoning.

