with this agitation, delirium, drowsy,

772
00:32:17.580 --> 00:32:19.710
there are tremors, they're hyperreflexic,

773
00:32:19.710 --> 00:32:23.760
and it's due to too much either SSRIs;

774
00:32:23.760 --> 00:32:26.280
or if they start combining SSRIs

775
00:32:26.280 --> 00:32:28.500
with cocaine or dextromethorphan

776
00:32:28.500 --> 00:32:31.410
or tramadol or linezolid,

777
00:32:31.410 --> 00:32:33.990
these will give you the serotonin syndrome.

778
00:32:33.990 --> 00:32:37.500
This is what it looks like. They're very sweaty.

779
00:32:37.500 --> 00:32:39.357
And that's a big difference between that

780
00:32:39.357 --> 00:32:40.440
and the anticholinergics.

781
00:32:40.440 --> 00:32:43.830
They're sweaty, tremorless, autonomic instability.

782
00:32:43.830 --> 00:32:46.620
And, again, this is the big differential between the two.

783
00:32:46.620 --> 00:32:48.450
The skin and serotonin syndrome,

784
00:32:48.450 --> 00:32:49.980
they're just sweating like crazy

785
00:32:49.980 --> 00:32:54.960
and you're dry, dry, dry, dry in anticholinergic syndrome.

786
00:32:54.960 --> 00:32:56.550
And the treatment for the serotonin syndrome

787
00:32:56.550 --> 00:32:57.420
is cyproheptadine.

788
00:32:57.420 --> 00:32:59.520
It's only orally available, no IV.

789
00:32:59.520 --> 00:33:01.809
And I'm gonna say thank you very much.

